  now uses surgery.arch_config.r_relative for the target architecture
- Replace silent x86_64 fallback in get_arch_config with a ValueError
  so unsupported machine types fail fast with a clear error message
- Add tests for ArchConfig/get_arch_config and the r_relative parameter
  on RelaEntry.get_target_address() and targets_range()

